01:33:08.974 --> 01:33:12.794
active humility to kind of embarrass...
"I have no control over anything. Stop

01:33:12.834 --> 01:33:14.654
telling me I'm the greatest
thing since sliced bread."

01:33:15.094 --> 01:33:18.714
- I like the leaders, and there's
